    // (Drill Template entries removed \u2014 folded into each Mount card's "Drill template PDFs" spec row.
    //  9 templates (A \u00B7 B \u00B7 C \u00B7 D \u00B7 E + 150W/200W/300W variants \u00B7 F) live in
    //  /02-OUTDOOR/luxo\u24B6RCH/LSBX-Shoebox/PACKAGING/HERITAGE/Drill Template/.
    //  A\u2013F-letter-code \u2192 SKU-mount-adder mapping is engineering-pending.)
