  //   This map MUST NOT carry inventory counts, warehouse breakdowns, or
  //   any trade-pricing tier (Rate / FFA / SPA / Tier 1). All such values
  //   belong in internal Zoho Books only \u2014 surfacing them in the public
  //   PDP exposes margin structure to competitors and breaks reseller
  //   agreements. The map below carries ONLY product-state metadata that
  //   a public spec writer can already infer from the catalog SKU itself:
  //     - whether the SKU is a known catalog item (vs Made-to-Order)
  //     - human-readable description of what the bundle includes
  //     - sensor technology variant on /BLS (Microwave on /RS \u00B7 PIR on /UA)
  //       (this is product-level fact, not commercial-data)
  //   Refresh: run 'mcp__zoho_books__list_items' with search_text='LSBX3W150'
  //   (or '300'), pull the SKU + name + is_combo_product flag ONLY.
  //   Do not pull or persist stock_on_hand / cf_midwest_* / rate / cf_ffa / etc.
  var ZOHO_CATALOG = {
    'LSBX3W150-3H1-UD3/RB3': {
      type: 'bare',
      name: 'Heritage-I \u00B7 150W Max \u00B7 Type-III \u00B7 Dark Bronze',
      sensorVariant: null
